OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with spells of rain,
OL,6,Flocally heavy, moving erratically
OL,7,Fnortheastwards across all parts during
OL,8,FThursday morning. Rain easing into the
OL,9,Fafternoon with some sunny intervals
OL,10,Falong the coast. Warm and muggy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain in the north clears
OL,13,Fduring the evening with cloud
OL,14,Flingering in the west, reasonable
OL,15,Fbreaks in the cloud develop in the
OL,16,Feast. Winds light but breezy along the
OL,17,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
