OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSunny in the east at first
OL,6,Fbefore cloud and rain spreads
OL,7,Feastwards across all parts by mid-
OL,8,Fafternoon. Feeling warmer than of late.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,11,FChangeable on Saturday with some
OL,12,Fspells of rain or showers moving
OL,13,Ferratically eastwards. Perhaps drier
OL,14,Fwith warm sunny spells Sunday and
OL,15,FMonday with temperatures climbing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
